moji\" />"},{"pid":"dacd536bcbb52f8eb4946ba6f179d276f3c2328b","tid":1697910,"uid":226829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9e722b8f0449f26c7b1c0904c9a37ffbbe0dd70","tid":1697910,"uid":48947,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T14:55:25.000Z","msg":"你話打飛機都好<br />\n的而且確有好幾個玄學post都推斷23-24年倒台"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T18:21:13.000Z","msg":"90年代，夠有大把玄學傳言推斷，臨近97時，支那會因為一個大人物既死而內戰，令到冇得如期97、99年收港澳，要押後，仲話內戰之後就走向民主化。<br />\n<br />\n97年2月，矮仔鄧終於去見老毛馬克思，我仲以為真係黎料，結果？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲記唔記得<br />\n千年蟲、2012，都話會世界末日？<br />\nJohn Titor 嗰D 2004年後再冇奧運、2005年美國內戰？<br />\n<br />\n傳到慶恰恰既預言，有邊樣中過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n反而隔離post既關帝乩文，就真係似層層<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf54120c995344755dbb8e9d4fd68f15f2618cab","tid":1697910,"uid":48947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dacd536bcbb52f8eb4946ba6f179d276f3c2328b","tid":1697910,"uid":226829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9e722b8f0449f26c7b1c0904c9a37ffbbe0dd70","tid":1697910,"uid":48947,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T14:55:25.000Z","msg":"你話打飛機都好<br />\n的而且確有好幾個玄學post都推斷23-24年倒台"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T18:21:13.000Z","msg":"90年代，夠有大把玄學傳言推斷，臨近97時，支那會因為一個大人物既死而內戰，令到冇得如期97、99年收港澳，要押後，仲話內戰之後就走向民主化。<br />\n<br />\n97年2月，矮仔鄧終於去見老毛馬克思，我仲以為真係黎料，結果？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲記唔記得<br />\n千年蟲、2012，都話會世界末日？<br />\nJohn Titor 嗰D 2004年後再冇奧運、2005年美國內戰？<br />\n<br />\n傳到慶恰恰既預言，有邊樣中過？<img src=\"/asset